>
> One work around for a small struct like that is to declare 4 arrays.
> e.g.
>
> class ALLEGRO_TRANSFORM < FFI::Struct
> =A0 =A0layout :m0, [:float, 4], :m1, [:float, 4], :m2, [:float, 4], :m3, =
